OL,7,FThat means checking his sales records
OL,8,Fbalance with takings and whatever
OL,9,Fstock he has left.
OL,11,FNasar has been running this post
OL,12,Foffice in Sheffield for the past three
OL,13,Fyears.
OL,15,FWith it he inherited Horizon
OL,16,Faccounting software and, he says,
OL,17,Fincreasingly regular unexplained
OL,18,Fshortfalls.
