OL,7,FHe said: "Ok this is the moment of
OL,8,Ftruth. That's telling us we're #2 out,
OL,9,Fit's not the biggest loss but it's a
OL,10,Floss."
OL,12,FNasar's biggest loss was back in 2022
OL,13,Fwhen nearly #5,000 disappeared from
OL,14,Fhis accounts.
OL,16,FThe Post Office investigated and
OL,17,Feventually cancelled that debt, but
OL,18,Fsays he still owes it thousands of
OL,19,Fpounds.
