OL,7,FHis most recent shortfall of #600 was
OL,8,Fjust last month.
OL,10,F"We're hemorrhaging money we don't
OL,11,Fhave, and it's becoming more frequent
OL,12,Fand the stress, mental anxiety,
OL,13,Fpressure that comes with this is just
OL,14,Fphenomenal," he said.
OL,16,FThe Post Office says it has visited
OL,17,FNasar's branch three times and offered
OL,18,Fextra training to him and his
OL,19,Fcolleagues.
