OL,7,FBut they aren't the only ones having
OL,8,Fproblems.
OL,10,FMark Harrison is already claiming
OL,11,Fagainst the Post Office for #20,000 of
OL,12,Fhistorical losses, but says things
OL,13,Fstill aren't adding up.
OL,15,FSince 2017 he estimates he's lost a
OL,16,Ffurther #5,000 - most of which he says
OL,17,Fhe's put back in the till out of his
OL,18,Fown pocket.
