OL,7,FSub-postmaster Mark Harrison said:
OL,8,F"Horizon isn't fit for what it does.
OL,9,FOne of my most recent ones was where
OL,10,Fwe had duplicate transactions on the
OL,11,Fscreen. Flagged it up to my area
OL,12,Fmanager and have heard nothing since."
OL,14,FThe Post Office says its area manager
OL,15,Fhas visited the branch and asks Mark
OL,16,Fto call its support centre for advice.
OL,18,FBut according to a postmasters
OL,19,Fcampaign group, his experience echoes
OL,20,Fhundreds of others.
