OL,7,FPostmaster Jerry Brown said: "Every
OL,8,Fday I see someone saying they are x
OL,9,Famount of pounds short. Post Office
OL,10,Flimited has to change now I believe
OL,11,Fbecause they are still gas lighting us
OL,12,Fevery day."
OL,14,FThe Post Office insists the current
OL,15,Fversion of Horizon is robust, but says
OL,16,Fit does intend to replace it.
OL,18,FIn the meantime - there are still sub-
OL,19,Fpostmasters who claim it is costing
OL,20,Fthem.
